body_html: I think that is mostly the problem... the shapes need to be the same.. Usually the train_input_fn and eval_input_fn return a batch_size full of data to process. Look into methods like https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/learn/python/learn/learn_io/graph_io.py#L434 (and more methods in that file).
